{"id": "art-1236", "label": "Art. 1236", "title": "Art. 1236: Condiţii", "slug": "art-1236", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 1236: Condi&#355;ii </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(1)Cauza trebuie s&#259; existe,\ns&#259; fie licit&#259; &#351;i moral&#259;.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(2)Cauza este ilicit&#259; când este\ncontrar&#259; legii &#351;i ordinii publice.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(3)Cauza este imoral&#259; când este\ncontrar&#259; bunelor moravuri.</span></p>"}